quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  10,61,Futhi asikho isimo obhekene naso noma ukufunda iQur’an futhi (abantu) abangawenzi umsebenzi ngaphandle kokuthi thina singofakazi kunina uma nizibandakanya kuwona (umsebenzi) futhi akukho lutho olufihlekile eNkosini yakho ngisho noma ngabe luncane kangakanani kulomhlaba noma ezulwini futhi noma ngabe luncane kakhulu kangakanani kunalokho ngisho noma lukhulu kakhulu kangakanani kepha (kulotshiwe) encwadini ecacile
  10,62,"Ngokungangabazeki, ngempela abangani baMvelinqangi akukho ukwesaba kubona futhi bona angeke baphatheke kabi"
  10,63,Yilabo abakholwayo (ebunyeni bukaMvelinqangi) futhi ababemesaba uMvelinqangi
  10,64,"Okwabo yizindaba ezimnandi (iphupho) empilweni yakulomhlaba nasempilweni ezayo, akukho ukuguqulwa kwamazwi kaMvelinqangi, lokho kungukuphumelela okukhulu"
  10,65,"Futhi ayingakuphathi kabi inkulumo yabo, ngempela ukuhlonipheka kungokukaMvelinqangi konke, yena ungozwayo owaziyo"
  10,66,"Ngokungangabazeki, ngempela bangabakaMvelinqangi bonke abasemazulwini nabobonke abasemhlabeni futhi abakulandeli (lokho) labo abamemeza abanye esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi (ababizwa ngokuthi) bangabakhonzi bezithixo, abalandeli lutho ngaphandle kwemicabango futhi abaqambi lutho ngaphandle kwamanga"
  10,67,"Nguyena owanenzela ubusuku ukuze niphumule kukona, nemini ukuze nibone ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu kubantu abalalelayo"
  10,68,"Bathi, “uMvelinqangi unendodana” udumo malube kuye! Yena akaswele lutho kungokwakhe okusemazulwini nakho konke okusemhlabeni, aninalo igunya (lokusho) lokhu, ngakube nisho ngoMvelinqangi lokho eningakwazi na"
  10,69,"Ithi, “ngempela labo abaqambela uMvelinqangi amanga angeke baphunyeleliswe”"
  10,70,Yinjabulo kulomhlaba bese kuba kukuthina ukubuyela kwabo bese sibezwisa isijeziso esinzima ngenxa yokuthi babengakholwa